\plain\fs22\tab\plain\b\fs22 ESCROW AGREEMENT \plain\fs22 made this {\strike ____}{\b\uldb 20}\plain\fs22\super {\b\uldb th}\plain\fs22  day of April, 2001 (the \ldblquote \plain\fs22\ul Escrow Agreement\plain\fs22\rdblquote ) among {\strike CITIBANK, N.A. (\ldblquote Escrow Agent\rdblquote ) and the undersigned} PEGASUS POWER PARTNERS, LLC (\ldblquote \plain\fs22\ul PPL\plain\fs22\rdblquote ) and ENRON NORTH AMERICA CORP. (\ldblquote \plain\fs22\ul ENA\plain\fs22\rdblquote ) (collectively the \ldblquote \plain\fs22\ul Depositors\plain\fs22\rdblquote  and individually a \ldblquote \plain\fs22\ul Depositor\plain\fs22\rdblquote ){\b\uldb , CITIBANK, N.A., as escrow agent (\ldblquote }\plain\fs22\ul {\b\uldb Escrow Agent}\plain\fs22{\b\uldb \rdblquote ), CITIBANK, N.A., as intermediary (the \ldblquote }\plain\fs22\ul {\b\uldb Intermediary}\plain\fs22{\b\uldb \rdblquote ), and US Bank Trust National Association, as collateral agent (the \ldblquote }\plain\fs22\ul {\b\uldb Collateral Agent}\plain\fs22{\b\uldb \rdblquote ).}\par 
\par 
\tab {\strike Depositors and Escrow Agent} {\b\uldb The parties} hereby agree that, in consideration of the mutual promises and covenants contained herein, Escrow Agent shall hold in escrow and shall distribute Escrow Property (as defined herein) in accordance with and subject to the following Instructions and Terms and Conditions:\par 
\par 
\pard\qc\frmtxlrtb\plain\b\fs22 I.  INSTRUCTIONS:\par 
\pard\qj\frmtxlrtb\plain\fs22\ul\par 
\plain\b\fs22 1.\tab\plain\b\fs22\ul Escrow Property\par 
\plain\fs22\ul\par 
\pard\qj\li720\frmtxlrtb\plain\fs22 The property and/or funds deposited or to be deposited with Escrow Agent by Depositors shall be as follows:\par 
\pard\qj\frmtxlrtb\par 
\pard\qj\li720\frmtxlrtb Cash in the amount of Sixty-Seven Million Seven Hundred Seventy-Six Thousand Seven Hundred and No/100 Dollars ($67,776,700.00) for {\b\uldb the direct benefit of PPL to provide financing for} Salmon Energy, LLC to acquire rights and obligations associated with the purchase of four LM6000 Enhanced {\strike dual-fuel} {\b\uldb Sprint} combustion turbine generator sets{\b\uldb , which amounts will be credited to the Account (as defined in paragraph 7, Part I).}\par 
\pard\qj\frmtxlrtb\par 
\pard\qj\li720\frmtxlrtb The foregoing property and/or funds, plus all interest, dividends and other distributions and payments thereon (collectively the \ldblquote \plain\fs22\ul Distributions\plain\fs22\rdblquote ) received by Escrow Agent, less any property and/or funds distributed or paid in accordance with this Escrow Agreement, are collectively referred to herein as \ldblquote \plain\fs22\ul Escrow Property\plain\fs22\rdblquote .  The Escrow Agent shall have no duty to solicit the Escrow Property.\par 
\pard\qj\frmtxlrtb\par 
\pard\qj\fi-720\li720\frmtxlrtb\plain\b\fs22 2.\tab\plain\b\fs22\ul Investment of Escrow Property\plain\fs22  \plain\b\fs22  \plain\fs22 (Depositors are to select one of the following options, mark the option selected and, if \ldblquote (b)\rdblquote  is selected, insert the appropriate information.)\par 
\pard\qj\frmtxlrtb\par 
\pard\qj\li720\frmtxlrtb\plain\fs22\ul\tab\plain\fs22  (a)\tab Escrow Agent shall have no obligation to pay interest on or to invest or reinvest any Escrow Property deposited or received hereunder.\par 
\pard\qj\frmtxlrtb\par 
\pard\qj\li720\frmtxlrtb\plain\fs22\ul      X\tab\plain\fs22  (b)\tab Escrow Agent shall invest or reinvest Escrow Property, without distinction between principal and income, in accordance with written instructions from PPL and ENA delivered to the Escrow Agent specifying any one or more of the following investments: \par 
\pard\qj\frmtxlrtb\par 
\pard\qj\li720\frmtxlrtb (1) Any U.S. Government agency or U.S. Government security;\par 
(2) Any commercial paper rated A1/P1 or better {\b\uldb by Standard & Poor\rquote s and Moody\rquote s};\par 
(3) A Money Market fund governed under the 1940 Act;{\strike  or\par }\par 
(4) The Citibank Insured Money Market Deposit Account{\b\uldb ; or\par 
(5) First American Treasury Obligation Fund (USBank).}{\strike \par }\par 
\par 
In the absence of written instructions, and after 11:00 a.m. (E.S.T.), the Escrow Agent is authorized to invest {\strike 50% of} the Escrow Property in {\strike the Dreyfus Money Market Fund titled Cash Management Investor Class (670) and 50% of the Escrow Property in Treasury Cash Management Investor Class (673).}{\b\uldb _______________________________________.}\par 
\par 
\softpage The Escrow Agent shall have no obligation to invest or reinvest the Escrow Property if deposited with the Escrow Agent after 11:00 a.m. (E.S.T.) on such day of deposit.  Instructions received after 11:00 a.m. (E.S.T.) will be treated as if received on the following business day.\par 
\par 
The Escrow Agent shall have the power to sell or liquidate the foregoing investments whenever the Escrow Agent shall be required to release the Escrow Property pursuant to the terms hereof. Requests (or instructions) received after 11:00 a.m. (E.S.T.) by the Escrow Agent to liquidate the Escrow Property will be treated as if received on the following business day.  The Escrow Agent shall have no responsibility for any investment losses resulting from the investment, reinvestment or liquidation of the Escrow Property {\b\uldb unless caused by its own willful misconduct or gross negligence}.  Any interest or other income received on such investment and reinvestment of the Escrow Property shall become part of the Escrow Property. {\strike If a selection is not made, the Escrow Property shall remain uninvested with no liability for interest therein.}  It is agreed and understood that the Escrow Agent may earn fees associated with the investments outlined above.\par 
\par 
Escrow Agent shall have no liability for any loss arising from or related to any such investment other than in accordance with paragraph 5 of the Terms and Conditions.\par 
\pard\qj\frmtxlrtb\par 
\plain\b\fs22 3.\tab\plain\b\fs22\ul Distribution of Escrow Property \plain\b\fs22\par 
\plain\fs22\par 
\pard\qj\li720\frmtxlrtb {\b\uldb In the absence of an entitlement order received by the Intermediary from the Collateral Agent,} Escrow Agent is directed to distribute the Escrow Property only in the following manner:\par 
\par 
\pard\qj\fi-720\li1440\frmtxlrtb (a)\tab Upon receipt of written instructions signed by both Depositors and otherwise in form and substance satisfactory to Escrow Agent, in accordance with such instructions;\par 
\pard\qj\li720\frmtxlrtb\par 
\pard\qj\fi-720\li1440\frmtxlrtb (b)\tab As permitted by this Escrow Agreement, to Escrow Agent;{\strike  or \par }\par 
\par 
